  <brief_title>D-chiro-Inositol in Overweight Type 1 Diabetes Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Pilot Study of D-Chiro-Inositol Plus Folic Acid in Overweight Patients With Type 1 Diabetes</official_title>
  <sponsors>
